{
  "video_id": "Tmk7nAvpMXQ",
  "title": "Can clouds buy us more time to solve climate change? | Kate Marvel",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12725.0,
      "end_time": 14454.0,
      "text": "I am a climate scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15340.0,
      "end_time": 17797.0,
      "text": "and I hate weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17821.0,
      "end_time": 20227.0,
      "text": "I have spent too much time in California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20251.0,
      "end_time": 23916.0,
      "text": "and I strongly feel that weather should be optional."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23940.0,
      "end_time": 25740.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25980.0,
      "end_time": 28139.0,
      "text": "So I don&#39;t want to experience clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28163.0,
      "end_time": 29536.0,
      "text": "let alone study them."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30186.0,
      "end_time": 33883.0,
      "text": "But clouds seem to follow me wherever I go."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34642.0,
      "end_time": 39123.0,
      "text": "The thing is, clouds are a real challenge for climate science."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39791.0,
      "end_time": 43611.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know how they&#39;re going to react as the planet heats up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43636.0,
      "end_time": 47357.0,
      "text": "and hidden in that uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47381.0,
      "end_time": 48667.0,
      "text": "might be hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49351.0,
      "end_time": 51884.0,
      "text": "Maybe, just maybe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51908.0,
      "end_time": 54589.0,
      "text": "clouds could slow down global warming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54613.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "and buy us a little bit more time to get our act together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58284.0,
      "end_time": 61000.0,
      "text": "which would be very convenient right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61420.0,
      "end_time": 65510.0,
      "text": "I mean, even I could put up with a few more cloudy days"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65534.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67601.0,
      "text": "if clouds saved the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68542.0,
      "end_time": 71970.0,
      "text": "Now, we are sure about some things."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71717.0,
      "end_time": 74390.0,
      "text": "Carbon dioxide is a greenhouse gas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74640.0,
      "end_time": 75460.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re emitting a lot of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75484.0,
      "end_time": 77300.0,
      "text": "and the planet is heating up."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77354.0,
      "end_time": 78666.0,
      "text": "Case closed."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79327.0,
      "end_time": 81182.0,
      "text": "But I still go to work every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81790.0,
      "end_time": 85490.0,
      "text": "It turns out that there is a lot that we don&#39;t understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85514.0,
      "end_time": 86981.0,
      "text": "about climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87434.0,
      "end_time": 89898.0,
      "text": "In particular, we haven&#39;t answered"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89922.0,
      "end_time": 92806.0,
      "text": "what seems to be a very fundamental question."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93404.0,
      "end_time": 94994.0,
      "text": "We know it&#39;s going to get hot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95190.0,
      "end_time": 98738.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t know exactly how hot it&#39;s going to get."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99492.0,
      "end_time": 102431.0,
      "text": "Now, this is a really easy question to answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102455.0,
      "end_time": 105429.0,
      "text": "if one of you would like to give me a time machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105453.0,
      "end_time": 107914.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m going to be honest with you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107938.0,
      "end_time": 109993.0,
      "text": "if I had a time machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110170.0,
      "end_time": 113303.0,
      "text": "I would not be hanging out at this particular point in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 114490.0,
      "end_time": 117102.0,
      "text": "So in order to see the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117126.0,
      "end_time": 120740.0,
      "text": "we have to rely on the output of computer simulations --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 120764.0,
      "end_time": 122726.0,
      "text": "climate models, like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123338.0,
      "end_time": 125178.0,
      "text": "Now, in my line of work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125202.0,
      "end_time": 128902.0,
      "text": "I encounter many very charming people on the internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 128925.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133630.0,
      "text": "who like to tell me that climate models are all wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133762.0,
      "end_time": 136780.0,
      "text": "And I would just like to say:"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136102.0,
      "end_time": 137286.0,
      "text": "no kidding!"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 138209.0,
      "end_time": 141787.0,
      "text": "Seriously? I get paid to complain about climate models."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141811.0,
      "end_time": 145172.0,
      "text": "But we don&#39;t want models to be perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 145645.0,
      "end_time": 147140.0,
      "text": "We want them to be useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147766.0,
      "end_time": 149397.0,
      "text": "I mean, think about it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 149421.0,
      "end_time": 151478.0,
      "text": "a computer simulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151503.0,
      "end_time": 155388.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s able to exactly reproduce all of reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 155986.0,
      "end_time": 157774.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not a climate model;"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 158315.0,
      "end_time": 159887.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s \"The Matrix.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 160842.0,
      "end_time": 164254.0,
      "text": "So, models are not crystal balls."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164278.0,
      "end_time": 165969.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re research tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 165993.0,
      "end_time": 170243.0,
      "text": "and the ways in which they&#39;re wrong can actually teach us a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170813.0,
      "end_time": 172166.0,
      "text": "For example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172190.0,
      "end_time": 175184.0,
      "text": "different climate models are largely able to capture"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 175208.0,
      "end_time": 177332.0,
      "text": "the warming that we&#39;ve seen so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 177356.0,
      "end_time": 180124.0,
      "text": "But fast-forward to the end of the century"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 180148.0,
      "end_time": 182477.0,
      "text": "under a business-as-usual scenario,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 182501.0,
      "end_time": 185270.0,
      "text": "and climate models don&#39;t really agree anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185607.0,
      "end_time": 188799.0,
      "text": "Yeah, they&#39;re all warming; that&#39;s just basic physics."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 189150.0,
      "end_time": 192359.0,
      "text": "But some of them project catastrophe --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 192383.0,
      "end_time": 195234.0,
      "text": "more than five times the warming we&#39;ve seen already."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195576.0,
      "end_time": 198161.0,
      "text": "And others are literally more chill."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 198839.0,
      "end_time": 203663.0,
      "text": "So why don&#39;t climate models agree on how warm it&#39;s going to get?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204254.0,
      "end_time": 206301.0,
      "text": "Well, to a large extent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 206325.0,
      "end_time": 209905.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s because they don&#39;t agree on what clouds will do in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 210572.0,
      "end_time": 213343.0,
      "text": "And that is because, just like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 213367.0,
      "end_time": 215203.0,
      "text": "computers hate clouds."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 215639.0,
      "end_time": 219829.0,
      "text": "Computers hate clouds because they&#39;re simultaneously very large"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 219853.0,
      "end_time": 221990.0,
      "text": "and very small."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 221624.0,
      "end_time": 222781.0,
      "text": "Clouds are formed"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222806.0,
      "end_time": 227431.0,
      "text": "when microscopic water droplets or ice crystals coalesce"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 227455.0,
      "end_time": 229410.0,
      "text": "around tiny particles."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 229515.0,
      "end_time": 233233.0,
      "text": "But at the same time, they cover two-thirds of the earth&#39;s surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 233715.0,
      "end_time": 236735.0,
      "text": "In order to really accurately model clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236759.0,
      "end_time": 241283.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d need to track the behavior of every water droplet and dust grain"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 241307.0,
      "end_time": 242749.0,
      "text": "in the entire atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 242773.0,
      "end_time": 245274.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s no computer powerful enough to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 245676.0,
      "end_time": 248436.0,
      "text": "So instead, we have to make a trade-off:"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 248940.0,
      "end_time": 251843.0,
      "text": "we can zoom in and get the details right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 251867.0,
      "end_time": 254845.0,
      "text": "but have no idea what&#39;s going on worldwide;"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 254869.0,
      "end_time": 259791.0,
      "text": "or, we could sacrifice realism at small scales"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 259815.0,
      "end_time": 261738.0,
      "text": "in order to see the bigger picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 262129.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264359.0,
      "text": "Now, there&#39;s no one right answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 264383.0,
      "end_time": 265938.0,
      "text": "no perfect way to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 266422.0,
      "end_time": 269364.0,
      "text": "and different climate models make different choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 270263.0,
      "end_time": 272628.0,
      "text": "Now, it is unfortunate"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 272652.0,
      "end_time": 274990.0,
      "text": "that computers struggle with clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 275140.0,
      "end_time": 277712.0,
      "text": "because clouds are crucially important"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277736.0,
      "end_time": 280870.0,
      "text": "in regulating the temperature of the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 280454.0,
      "end_time": 283250.0,
      "text": "In fact, if all the clouds went away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 283490.0,
      "end_time": 286169.0,
      "text": "we would experience profound climate changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 286809.0,
      "end_time": 288282.0,
      "text": "But without clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 288306.0,
      "end_time": 290570.0,
      "text": "would it be warmer or colder?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 291312.0,
      "end_time": 292872.0,
      "text": "The answer is both."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 293836.0,
      "end_time": 296858.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to be honest with you, I am not a cloud spotter."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 296882.0,
      "end_time": 299152.0,
      "text": "My favorite type of cloud is none."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 299590.0,
      "end_time": 303695.0,
      "text": "But even I know that clouds come in all shapes and sizes."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304387.0,
      "end_time": 308607.0,
      "text": "Low, thick clouds like these are really good at blocking out the sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 308631.0,
      "end_time": 310250.0,
      "text": "and ruining your barbecue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 310708.0,
      "end_time": 313631.0,
      "text": "and high, wispy clouds like these cirrus"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 313655.0,
      "end_time": 315876.0,
      "text": "largely let that sunlight stream through."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 316436.0,
      "end_time": 318832.0,
      "text": "Every sunny day is the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318857.0,
      "end_time": 321340.0,
      "text": "but every cloudy day is cloudy in its own way."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 321857.0,
      "end_time": 323815.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s this diversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323839.0,
      "end_time": 327644.0,
      "text": "that can make the global impact of clouds very hard to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 328960.0,
      "end_time": 331100.0,
      "text": "So to see this global effect of clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 331124.0,
      "end_time": 333767.0,
      "text": "it really helps to take a selfie."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 334958.0,
      "end_time": 338459.0,
      "text": "It will never cease to blow my mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 338483.0,
      "end_time": 341310.0,
      "text": "that we can see our planet from outer space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 341692.0,
      "end_time": 343333.0,
      "text": "but we can&#39;t see all of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 343938.0,
      "end_time": 345578.0,
      "text": "Clouds are blocking the view."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 346120.0,
      "end_time": 347485.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what they do."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 347509.0,
      "end_time": 352195.0,
      "text": "These low, thick clouds are extremely effective sunshades."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 352219.0,
      "end_time": 355783.0,
      "text": "They turn back about 20 percent of everything the sun sends us."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 356294.0,
      "end_time": 358998.0,
      "text": "That is a lot of wasted solar power."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 359220.0,
      "end_time": 362400.0,
      "text": "So, low clouds are powerful sunshades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 362280.0,
      "end_time": 363868.0,
      "text": "making the planet cooler."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 363892.0,
      "end_time": 366610.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not the only effect of clouds."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 366766.0,
      "end_time": 368338.0,
      "text": "Our planet has a temperature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 368362.0,
      "end_time": 370549.0,
      "text": "and like anything with a temperature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 370573.0,
      "end_time": 371918.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s giving off heat."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 372469.0,
      "end_time": 375795.0,
      "text": "We are radiating thermal energy away into space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 375819.0,
      "end_time": 378664.0,
      "text": "and we can see this in the infrared."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 378688.0,
      "end_time": 381799.0,
      "text": "Once again, clouds are blocking the view."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 382207.0,
      "end_time": 386100.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because high clouds live in the upper reaches of the atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 386340.0,
      "end_time": 387407.0,
      "text": "where it&#39;s very cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 387811.0,
      "end_time": 391508.0,
      "text": "And this means that they lose very little heat to space themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 391533.0,
      "end_time": 395924.0,
      "text": "But at the same time, they block the heat coming up from the planet below."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 395948.0,
      "end_time": 398823.0,
      "text": "The earth is trying to cool itself off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 398847.0,
      "end_time": 401356.0,
      "text": "and high clouds are getting in the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 401983.0,
      "end_time": 406570.0,
      "text": "The result is a very powerful greenhouse effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 406819.0,
      "end_time": 410673.0,
      "text": "So, clouds play this very large and dual role"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 410697.0,
      "end_time": 412268.0,
      "text": "in the climate system."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 412292.0,
      "end_time": 415820.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got low clouds that act like a sunshade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 415107.0,
      "end_time": 416476.0,
      "text": "cooling the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 416500.0,
      "end_time": 419419.0,
      "text": "and high clouds which act like a greenhouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 419443.0,
      "end_time": 420628.0,
      "text": "warming the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 421245.0,
      "end_time": 424486.0,
      "text": "Right now, these two effects -- they don&#39;t cancel out."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 424510.0,
      "end_time": 427928.0,
      "text": "That sunshade -- it&#39;s a little bit more powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 427952.0,
      "end_time": 431300.0,
      "text": "So if we got rid of all the clouds tomorrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 431540.0,
      "end_time": 434268.0,
      "text": "which, for the record, I am not advocating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 434292.0,
      "end_time": 436121.0,
      "text": "our planet would get warmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 436875.0,
      "end_time": 440606.0,
      "text": "So clearly, all of the clouds are not going away."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 440630.0,
      "end_time": 442902.0,
      "text": "But climate change is change."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 443348.0,
      "end_time": 444758.0,
      "text": "So we can ask:"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 444782.0,
      "end_time": 447870.0,
      "text": "How will global warming change clouds?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 448696.0,
      "end_time": 451510.0,
      "text": "But remember, clouds are so important"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 451534.0,
      "end_time": 453632.0,
      "text": "in regulating the earth&#39;s temperature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 453656.0,
      "end_time": 456367.0,
      "text": "and they both warm and cool the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 456391.0,
      "end_time": 459471.0,
      "text": "So even small changes to cloud cover"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 459495.0,
      "end_time": 461576.0,
      "text": "could have profound consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 462600.0,
      "end_time": 464200.0,
      "text": "So we might also ask:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 464440.0,
      "end_time": 467152.0,
      "text": "How will clouds change global warming?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 467790.0,
      "end_time": 470847.0,
      "text": "And that is where there might be space for hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 471505.0,
      "end_time": 474709.0,
      "text": "If global warming triggers cloud changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 474733.0,
      "end_time": 479885.0,
      "text": "that make for a less powerful greenhouse or a more effective sunshade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 479909.0,
      "end_time": 483599.0,
      "text": "then that would enhance the cooling power of clouds."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 483623.0,
      "end_time": 487150.0,
      "text": "It would act in opposition to global warming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 487174.0,
      "end_time": 490144.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s what&#39;s happening in those climate models"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 490168.0,
      "end_time": 492661.0,
      "text": "that project relatively muted warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 493214.0,
      "end_time": 496577.0,
      "text": "But climate models struggle with clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 496601.0,
      "end_time": 499755.0,
      "text": "and this uncertainty -- it goes both ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 500412.0,
      "end_time": 502741.0,
      "text": "Clouds could help us out with global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 503653.0,
      "end_time": 505252.0,
      "text": "They could also make it worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 505953.0,
      "end_time": 508839.0,
      "text": "Now, we know that climate change is happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 508863.0,
      "end_time": 510628.0,
      "text": "because we can see it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 510652.0,
      "end_time": 516223.0,
      "text": "rising temperatures, melting icecaps, shifts in rainfall patterns."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 516701.0,
      "end_time": 520980.0,
      "text": "And you might think that we could also see it in the clouds."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 520121.0,
      "end_time": 522637.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s something else unfortunate:"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 522662.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525333.0,
      "text": "clouds are really hard to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 526254.0,
      "end_time": 528300.0,
      "text": "I see everybody from the Pacific Northwest"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 528324.0,
      "end_time": 530522.0,
      "text": "is like, \"I have some suggestions for you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 530547.0,
      "end_time": 531571.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 531595.0,
      "end_time": 534191.0,
      "text": "And you guys, we have tried looking up."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 534215.0,
      "end_time": 535266.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 535290.0,
      "end_time": 538309.0,
      "text": "But in order to do climate science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 538333.0,
      "end_time": 543466.0,
      "text": "we need to see all of the clouds, everywhere, for a very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 543490.0,
      "end_time": 545235.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what makes it hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 545917.0,
      "end_time": 550691.0,
      "text": "Now, nothing sees more clouds than a satellite --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 550715.0,
      "end_time": 552635.0,
      "text": "not even a British person."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 552659.0,
      "end_time": 553780.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 553804.0,
      "end_time": 558911.0,
      "text": "And fortunately, we do have satellite observations of clouds"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 558935.0,
      "end_time": 561799.0,
      "text": "that, like me, date back to the 1980s."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 562502.0,
      "end_time": 566116.0,
      "text": "But these satellites were designed for weather,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 566140.0,
      "end_time": 567664.0,
      "text": "not climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 567688.0,
      "end_time": 569602.0,
      "text": "They weren&#39;t in it for the long haul."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 569626.0,
      "end_time": 572312.0,
      "text": "So to get that long-term trend information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 572336.0,
      "end_time": 574111.0,
      "text": "we need to do climate science."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 574135.0,
      "end_time": 577253.0,
      "text": "We have to stitch together the output of multiple satellites"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 577277.0,
      "end_time": 580355.0,
      "text": "with different viewing angles and orbits"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 580379.0,
      "end_time": 582302.0,
      "text": "and carrying different camera equipment."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 582326.0,
      "end_time": 583548.0,
      "text": "And as a result,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 583572.0,
      "end_time": 585724.0,
      "text": "there are gaps in our knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 586319.0,
      "end_time": 589647.0,
      "text": "But even from this very cloudy picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 589672.0,
      "end_time": 592835.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re starting to get hints of a possible future."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 593468.0,
      "end_time": 596680.0,
      "text": "When we looked at the observations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 596920.0,
      "end_time": 597908.0,
      "text": "one thing jumped out at us:"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 598492.0,
      "end_time": 600521.0,
      "text": "the clouds are moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 601513.0,
      "end_time": 604200.0,
      "text": "As the planet&#39;s temperature increases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 605958.0,
      "text": "high clouds rise up."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 606506.0,
      "end_time": 610736.0,
      "text": "They move to the colder upper reaches of the atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 610760.0,
      "end_time": 614423.0,
      "text": "and this means that even as the planet heats up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 614447.0,
      "end_time": 615764.0,
      "text": "high clouds don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 616204.0,
      "end_time": 618840.0,
      "text": "They remain at roughly the same temperature."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 618865.0,
      "end_time": 622363.0,
      "text": "So they are not losing more heat to space."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 622387.0,
      "end_time": 625424.0,
      "text": "But at the same time, they&#39;re trapping more heat"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 625448.0,
      "end_time": 627180.0,
      "text": "from the warming planet below."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 627669.0,
      "end_time": 630669.0,
      "text": "This intensifies the greenhouse effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 631614.0,
      "end_time": 635360.0,
      "text": "High clouds are making global warming worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 636202.0,
      "end_time": 638667.0,
      "text": "Clouds are moving in other dimensions, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 638691.0,
      "end_time": 641696.0,
      "text": "The atmospheric circulation, that large-scale motion"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 641720.0,
      "end_time": 643638.0,
      "text": "of air and water in the atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 643662.0,
      "end_time": 645490.0,
      "text": "is changing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 645730.0,
      "end_time": 647337.0,
      "text": "and clouds are going with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 649360.0,
      "end_time": 650641.0,
      "text": "On large scales,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 650666.0,
      "end_time": 654778.0,
      "text": "clouds seem to be moving from the tropics toward the poles."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 654802.0,
      "end_time": 657339.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of like your grandparents in reverse."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 658270.0,
      "end_time": 659606.0,
      "text": "And this matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 659630.0,
      "end_time": 663479.0,
      "text": "because if your job is to block incoming sunlight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 663503.0,
      "end_time": 666519.0,
      "text": "you are going to be much more effective in the tropics"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 666543.0,
      "end_time": 668740.0,
      "text": "under that intense tropical sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 668764.0,
      "end_time": 670621.0,
      "text": "than you are in higher latitudes."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 671920.0,
      "end_time": 672962.0,
      "text": "So if this keeps up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 672986.0,
      "end_time": 676830.0,
      "text": "this will also make global warming worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 676107.0,
      "end_time": 678428.0,
      "text": "And what we have not found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 678452.0,
      "end_time": 680730.0,
      "text": "despite years of looking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 680754.0,
      "end_time": 683332.0,
      "text": "is any indication of the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 683865.0,
      "end_time": 686797.0,
      "text": "There is no observational evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 686821.0,
      "end_time": 690556.0,
      "text": "that clouds will substantially slow down global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 691961.0,
      "end_time": 695298.0,
      "text": "The earth is not going to break its own fever."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 696130.0,
      "end_time": 698449.0,
      "text": "Now, there are still uncertainties here."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 699440.0,
      "end_time": 701271.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know for sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 701296.0,
      "end_time": 702951.0,
      "text": "what the future holds."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 703671.0,
      "end_time": 706197.0,
      "text": "But we are sending our kids there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 706802.0,
      "end_time": 708800.0,
      "text": "and they are never coming back."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 710253.0,
      "end_time": 713384.0,
      "text": "I want them to be prepared for what they&#39;ll face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 714120.0,
      "end_time": 717363.0,
      "text": "and that is why it is so important"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 717387.0,
      "end_time": 720637.0,
      "text": "to keep our earth-observing satellites up there"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 720662.0,
      "end_time": 724458.0,
      "text": "and to hire diverse and smart and talented people"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 724482.0,
      "end_time": 726749.0,
      "text": "who do not hate clouds"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 726773.0,
      "end_time": 728708.0,
      "text": "to improve the climate models."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 729390.0,
      "end_time": 732913.0,
      "text": "But uncertainty is not ignorance."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 733873.0,
      "end_time": 735345.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 735913.0,
      "end_time": 737507.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t know nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 738254.0,
      "end_time": 740648.0,
      "text": "and we know what carbon dioxide does."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 741651.0,
      "end_time": 744814.0,
      "text": "I started my career as an astrophysicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 744839.0,
      "end_time": 746321.0,
      "text": "so you can believe me"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 746345.0,
      "end_time": 751802.0,
      "text": "when I say that this is the greatest place in the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 752904.0,
      "end_time": 755721.0,
      "text": "Other planets might have liquid water."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 756808.0,
      "end_time": 759951.0,
      "text": "On earth, we have whiskey."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 759975.0,
      "end_time": 761988.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 762120.0,
      "end_time": 767200.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 767440.0,
      "end_time": 770237.0,
      "text": "We are so lucky to live here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 771410.0,
      "end_time": 773504.0,
      "text": "but let&#39;s not push our luck."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 774296.0,
      "end_time": 777234.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think that clouds will save the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 778450.0,
      "end_time": 779733.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s probably up to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 780177.0,
      "end_time": 781416.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 781440.0,
      "end_time": 784390.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}